00:19:55.480  --> 00:19:58.610 position:50% line:94% align:middle 
腦中的她們只是一種意象


00:19:58.610  --> 00:20:01.360 position:50% line:94% align:middle 
變化效果終究只是變化效果


00:20:01.780  --> 00:20:03.660 position:50% line:94% align:middle 
沒錯, 這是…


00:20:04.110  --> 00:20:07.950 position:50% line:94% align:middle 
搖擺不定的少女之心的變化效果


00:20:09.200  --> 00:20:10.700 position:50% line:94% align:middle 
會長你寒假期間


00:20:10.950  --> 00:20:13.250 position:50% line:94% align:middle 
可以借我一天的時間嗎?


00:20:13.870  --> 00:20:14.750 position:50% line:94% align:middle 
可以啊


00:20:16.460  --> 00:20:17.840 position:50% line:94% align:middle 
我們一起去約會吧


00:20:17.840  --> 00:20:20.380 position:50% line:94% align:middle 
有些事我想用言語清楚地向你表達


00:20:21.760  --> 00:20:24.720 position:50% line:94% align:middle 
(12月27日)


00:20:25.720  --> 00:20:27.680 position:50% line:94% align:middle 
人為什麼要告白呢?


00:20:28.470  --> 00:20:29.810 position:50% line:94% align:middle 
總而言之


00:20:30.390  --> 00:20:32.730 position:50% line:94% align:middle 
(副業"假日占卜師")
可以先讓我看看妳的手相嗎?


00:20:33.980  --> 00:20:36.560 position:50% line:94% align:middle 
妳一定沒有什麼良好的戀愛經驗吧


00:20:37.230  --> 00:20:39.020 position:50% line:94% align:middle 
從手相就能看得出來嗎


00:20:39.440  --> 00:20:41.860 position:50% line:94% align:middle 
還有妳的個性很單純呢


00:20:41.860  --> 00:20:43.200 position:50% line:94% align:middle 
而且手相顯示


00:20:43.200  --> 00:20:46.110 position:50% line:94% align:middle 
妳只要一累積壓力就會衝動性購物


00:20:46.530  --> 00:20:47.490 position:50% line:94% align:middle 
好厲害


00:20:47.740  --> 00:20:49.370 position:50% line:94% align:middle 
他是真正的占卜師


00:20:49.700  --> 00:20:50.540 position:50% line:94% align:middle 
那麼


00:20:51.330  --> 00:20:54.670 position:50% line:94% align:middle 
妳剛才問人為什麼要告白是嗎


00:20:55.710  --> 00:20:56.420 position:50% line:94% align:middle 
是的


00:20:57.080  --> 00:20:57.880 position:50% line:94% align:middle 
你…


00:20:57.880  --> 00:21:00.340 position:50% line:94% align:middle 
你為什麼要穿便服出來約會啊


00:21:01.170  --> 00:21:03.130 position:50% line:94% align:middle 
約會一般不都是穿便服嗎


00:21:03.630  --> 00:21:06.510 position:50% line:94% align:middle 
會長不是時時刻刻都穿著立領制服嗎


00:21:06.510  --> 00:21:08.890 position:50% line:94% align:middle 
所以我才想配合你的啊


00:21:09.260  --> 00:21:11.390 position:50% line:94% align:middle 
為什麼偏偏在這種日子…


00:21:11.890  --> 00:21:13.560 position:50% line:94% align:middle 
不, 因為…


00:21:14.100  --> 00:21:16.440 position:50% line:94% align:middle 
就因為是這種日子吧


00:21:19.440  --> 00:21:20.400 position:50% line:94% align:middle 
我們走吧


00:21:21.440  --> 00:21:22.150 position:50% line:94% align:middle 
是


00:21:24.150  --> 00:21:26.950 position:50% line:94% align:middle 
大家總是輕易地就和人交往或分手


00:21:27.530  --> 00:21:30.030 position:50% line:94% align:middle 
對方或許是命中註定的對象


00:21:30.030  --> 00:21:32.040 position:50% line:94% align:middle 
或許是能一直喜歡下去的對象


00:21:32.040  --> 00:21:34.410 position:50% line:94% align:middle 
又或許能讓對方喜歡上自己


00:21:35.960  --> 00:21:37.870 position:50% line:94% align:middle 
如果喜歡的話待在對方身邊就好了


00:21:38.250  --> 00:21:41.210 position:50% line:94% align:middle 
如果討厭的話分開就好了


00:21:51.890  --> 00:21:53.220 position:50% line:94% align:middle 
你不覺得就是因為說出口


00:21:53.560  --> 00:21:55.680 position:50% line:94% align:middle 
事情才會變得這麼麻煩嗎


00:21:56.440  --> 00:21:58.100 position:50% line:94% align:middle 
也許真是如此吧


00:21:59.020  --> 00:21:59.810 position:50% line:94% align:middle 
但是


00:22:00.270  --> 00:22:03.280 position:50% line:94% align:middle 
能喜歡一個人到甚至變得愚笨的地步


00:22:03.280  --> 00:22:04.570 position:50% line:94% align:middle 
是很幸福的


00:22:05.190  --> 00:22:06.990 position:50% line:94% align:middle 
妳可以試著去體驗看看


00:22:09.820  --> 00:22:14.580 position:50% line:94% align:middle 
會想和喜歡的人成為情侶是很自然的事


00:22:15.870  --> 00:22:18.620 position:50% line:94% align:middle 
有時因為擔心被拒絕而膽戰心驚


00:22:19.790  --> 00:22:21.920 position:50% line:94% align:middle 
有時試著擬定攻防策略


00:22:23.590  --> 00:22:25.460 position:50% line:94% align:middle 
訂下各種計劃


00:22:25.460  --> 00:22:27.880 position:50% line:94% align:middle 
打算鎖定最佳時機展開行動


00:22:29.760  --> 00:22:33.010 position:50% line:94% align:middle 
卻因為小鹿亂撞使腦袋變得一團混亂


00:22:36.390  --> 00:22:38.020 position:50% line:94% align:middle 
在心想今天又要在


00:22:38.020  --> 00:22:40.440 position:50% line:94% align:middle 
沒能說出口的狀態下結束時


00:22:45.230  --> 00:22:46.440 position:50% line:94% align:middle 
我喜歡你


00:22:48.240  --> 00:22:50.610 position:50% line:94% align:middle 
請和我成為男女朋友


00:22:51.030  --> 00:22:53.530 position:50% line:94% align:middle 
話語也許就會脫口而出


00:22:54.200  --> 00:22:55.870 position:50% line:94% align:middle 
喜歡上一個人


00:22:55.870  --> 00:22:58.210 position:50% line:94% align:middle 
開口告白, 並成為情侶


00:22:58.710  --> 00:23:02.210 position:50% line:94% align:middle 
任誰都會說這是件很美好的事


00:23:02.670  --> 00:23:05.050 position:50% line:94% align:middle 
然而這是錯誤的


00:23:05.840  --> 00:23:09.590 position:50% line:94% align:middle 
戀愛最快樂的是開花結果前的過程


00:23:10.220  --> 00:23:12.640 position:50% line:94% align:middle 
一旦心意高漲至某個程度


00:23:12.640  --> 00:23:15.310 position:50% line:94% align:middle 
再來就會直直地往下掉


00:23:15.640  --> 00:23:18.390 position:50% line:94% align:middle 
那就是戀愛的真面目


00:23:19.060  --> 00:23:22.150 position:50% line:94% align:middle 
戀愛的終點不存在贏家或輸家


00:23:22.560  --> 00:23:24.820 position:50% line:94% align:middle 
無從得知對方是不是命中註定的對象


00:23:24.820  --> 00:23:27.360 position:50% line:94% align:middle 
永恆的愛或許也並不存在


00:23:28.240  --> 00:23:29.190 position:50% line:94% align:middle 
我知道了


00:23:31.200  --> 00:23:31.990 position:50% line:94% align:middle 
但是


00:23:32.360  --> 00:23:35.200 position:50% line:94% align:middle 
真正的愛或許是存在的


00:23:35.780  --> 00:23:37.540 position:50% line:94% align:middle 
我們需要的是頭腦


00:23:37.950  --> 00:23:41.540 position:50% line:94% align:middle 
如果想追求真正的愛就必須要懂得思考


00:23:41.540  --> 00:23:43.420 position:50% line:94% align:middle 
這不是什麼簡單的事情


00:23:43.420  --> 00:23:45.090 position:50% line:94% align:middle 
但是, 即使如此


00:23:45.090  --> 00:23:47.550 position:50% line:94% align:middle 
唯有懂得持續思考


00:23:49.050  --> 00:23:50.670 position:50% line:94% align:middle 
才能成為在這世界上


00:23:51.090  --> 00:23:54.180 position:50% line:94% align:middle 
最先掌握住真愛的人


00:24:16.450  --> 00:24:18.290 position:50% line:94% align:middle 
對不起


00:24:18.740  --> 00:24:26.790 position:50% line:94% align:middle 
將一切都怪罪於溫柔的你


00:24:28.800  --> 00:24:33.510 position:50% line:94% align:middle 
那困擾的側臉


00:24:34.340  --> 00:24:39.720 position:50% line:94% align:middle 
相信只有我可以化解


00:24:40.100  --> 00:24:41.850 position:50% line:94% align:middle 
在你的身邊


00:24:41.850  --> 00:24:45.940 position:50% line:94% align:middle 
心中彷彿已經快要凍僵的思念


00:24:46.270  --> 00:24:51.940 position:50% line:94% align:middle 
今天一定要好好率直地


00:24:52.610  --> 00:24:55.610 position:50% line:94% align:middle 
傳達給你知道


00:24:55.820  --> 00:25:00.240 position:50% line:94% align:middle 
我們總是能在迷惘之中


00:25:00.240  --> 00:25:03.080 position:50% line:94% align:middle 
邂逅彼此


00:25:03.080  --> 00:25:04.660 position:50% line:94% align:middle 
那所有的一切


00:25:04.660  --> 00:25:07.960 position:50% line:94% align:middle 
全是只屬於我的心意


00:25:07.960  --> 00:25:12.550 position:50% line:94% align:middle 
藏在我的心靈筆記中


00:25:12.550  --> 00:25:17.010 position:50% line:94% align:middle 
不論甜美還是苦澀


00:25:17.010  --> 00:25:21.890 position:50% line:94% align:middle 
願你能擁抱這一切

